# Screen Catalog'dan Kritik Ekran Uygulama (Detaylı)

Bu prosedür `41-add-new-screen.mdc`'yi detaylandırır. Kritik screen'ler için spec → code mapping section-by-section.

Temel prosedür için 41 rule'a bakıp, detaylı mapping için bu rule'u kullan.

**Görsel uygulama:** `docs/lean-design-system/` (token + `ls-*`) — `26-lean-design-system.mdc`; spec’teki layout ile birlikte düşün.

## Critical Screen Spec Sections → Code Mapping

Her Critical screen şu section'ları içerir. Her biri koda yansır:

### Section: Route, Access, Layout

| Spec field | Code implementation |
|---|---|
| Route: `/users/new` | `apps/web/src/app/(app)/users/new/page.tsx` |
| Access: Authenticated + Permission | Middleware + `<PermissionGate>` or layout guard |
| Layout: AppLayout | Route group `(app)/` |
| Level: Critical | Full template, E2E if in critical journey |

### Section: Visual Structure (Numbered Sections)

Spec'te örneğin:
1. Page title + breadcrumb
2. Form card
3. Action buttons (primary submit + cancel)
4. Error summary (if needed)

Kod'a mapping:

```typescript
// NewUserPage
<FormLayout
  title="Yeni Kullanıcı"           // 1: Page title
  breadcrumbs={[...]}               // 1: Breadcrumb
>
  <UserForm />                       // 2: Form card
</FormLayout>

// UserForm
<Form {...form}>
  <form onSubmit={form.handleSubmit(onSubmit)}>
    {/* Field 1-N */}
    <FormField ... />
    
    {/* Error summary — only if big form */}
    <ErrorSummary errors={form.formState.errors} />
    
    {/* Action buttons — 3 */}
    <div className="flex justify-end gap-2">
      <Button type="button" variant="outline">İptal</Button>
      <Button type="submit">Oluştur</Button>
    </div>
  </form>
</Form>
```

### Section: Data Source

Spec:
> **API**: `POST /api/v1/users`  
> **Query key**: `queryKeys.users.lists()` (for invalidation)  
> **Mutation key**: `useCreateUserMutation`  
> **Invalidate on success**: `queryKeys.users.lists()`

Kod:

```typescript
// lib/queries/users.ts
export function useCreateUserMutation() {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: (input: CreateUserInput) => 
      apiClient.post('/api/v1/users', input).then((r) => r.data.data),
    onSuccess: () => {
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.lists() });
    },
  });
}

// UserForm
const createUser = useCreateUserMutation();
```

### Section: State Management

Spec:
> **Server state**: None (create screen)  
> **Local state**: None  
> **URL state**: None (unless edit with params)  
> **Form state**: RHF — CreateUserSchema

Kod:

```typescript
const form = useForm<CreateUserInput>({
  resolver: zodResolver(CreateUserSchema),
  defaultValues: { /* all fields */ },
});
```

### Section: State Screens

Spec tablosu:

| Durum | UX |
|---|---|
| Initial | Form boş, focus ilk field'da |
| Submit in progress | Submit button disabled + spinner |
| Submit success | Toast "Kullanıcı oluşturuldu" + redirect `/users/:id` |
| Submit field error | Inline `<FormMessage>` field üstünde |
| Submit generic error | Toast hata mesajı |
| Unsaved changes exit attempt | `beforeunload` confirm |

Kod (partial):

```typescript
useUnsavedChangesWarning(form.formState.isDirty);

const onSubmit = async (values) => {
  try {
    const user = await createUser.mutateAsync(values);
    toast.success('Kullanıcı oluşturuldu');        // Success
    router.push(`/users/${user.id}`);              // Redirect
  } catch (err) {
    handleFormError(err, form);                    // Field or generic error
  }
};

<Button 
  type="submit" 
  disabled={form.formState.isSubmitting}           // In progress
>
  {form.formState.isSubmitting && <Loader2 />}
  Oluştur
</Button>
```

### Section: Interactions

Spec:
> - İlk field'a otomatik focus
> - Tab ile field'lar arası gez
> - Enter submit tetikler
> - İptal button → previous page (router.back())

Kod:

```typescript
// Auto-focus first field
const firstFieldRef = useRef<HTMLInputElement>(null);
useEffect(() => {
  firstFieldRef.current?.focus();
}, []);

<Input {...field} ref={firstFieldRef} />

// Enter submit — native form behavior (onSubmit)
// Tab navigation — native (correct DOM order)

// Cancel button
<Button type="button" variant="outline" onClick={() => router.back()}>
  İptal
</Button>
```

### Section: Edge Cases

Spec örnekleri:
> - Company dropdown empty (hiç company yoksa) → disable form + info mesajı
> - Manager seçimi için user list çok büyük → autocomplete
> - Email case-sensitivity: lowercase'e çevir submit'te
> - Sicil format validation failed → inline error

Her edge case kod'da handle:

```typescript
const { data: companies } = useCompaniesQuery();

if (!companies?.length) {
  return (
    <div className="p-6 text-center">
      <p className="text-muted-foreground">
        Kullanıcı oluşturmak için önce en az bir şirket tanımlanmalı.
      </p>
      <PermissionGate requires={Permission.MASTER_DATA_MANAGE}>
        <Button onClick={() => router.push('/admin/companies/new')}>
          Şirket Oluştur
        </Button>
      </PermissionGate>
    </div>
  );
}

// Email lowercase — Zod schema'da `.toLowerCase()` var, ek gerek yok
// Sicil validation — Zod regex, FormMessage otomatik
```

### Section: Form Fields (Form-Bearing Screens)

Spec tablosu:

| Field | Type | Validation | Default | Disabled When |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| sicil | text | 8 digit numeric | `''` | edit mode |
| firstName | text | 1-100 char | `''` | - |
| email | email | valid email | `''` | - |
| companyId | select | required uuid | `undefined` | - |
| managerUserId | select (autocomplete) | optional uuid | `undefined` | - |

Kod her row'u reflect eder — FormField + validation message + defaultValues + disabled prop.

